{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-fill-in-the-blank-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-first-questions/task-13","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"title":"Lekcija 13","description":"","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Ovaj vežbaji nema zvuk. Dopuni razgovor koji je dole.</p>\n<p>Napišite ove reči na odgovarajuće mesto:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">tú</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">es</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">mi</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tardes</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">hola</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">te</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">llamo</span></p>\n<p>Postoji više reči nego praznog prostora. Nije potrebno da koristiš sve reči.</p>\n</section>","explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Razgovor između Matea i Kamile sadrži ove uobičajene fraze:</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Cómo te llamas?</span> znači \"Jina lako nani?\" (obično).</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Mi nombre es...</span> to znači \"Moje ime je\".</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">¿Y tú?</span> znači \"A ti?\". Ovo se koristi za normalno ponavljanje pitanja.</p>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Me llamo...</span> je najčešći način da kažeš svoje ime.</p>\n</section>","challengeType":22,"helpCategory":"Spanish Curriculum","superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","block":"es-a1-practice-first-questions","lang":"es","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-first-questions/task-13"},"fillInTheBlank":{"sentence":"<p>Camila: Hola, buenas tardes. ¿Cómo BLANK llamas?</p>\n<p>Mateo: BLANK nombre es Mateo. ¿Y BLANK?</p>\n<p>Camila: Me BLANK Camila.</p>","blanks":[{"answer":"te","feedback":"<p>Ova reč se koristi sa glagolom <span class=\"highlighted-text\">llamarse</span> (\"nazvan\") za formu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">tú</span> (\"ti\").</p>"},{"answer":"Mi","feedback":"<p>Ovo je posesivna reč za prvo lice (\"moj\").</p>"},{"answer":"tú","feedback":"<p>Ovo je glagol koji se koristi za referisanje na drugo lice jednine u opštem kontekstu. Zapamtite da koristite crticu na slovo <span class=\"highlighted-text\">u</span>.</p>"},{"answer":"llamo","feedback":"<p>Ovo je oblik prvog lica u jedmini (<span class=\"highlighted-text\">yo</span>) glagola <span class=\"highlighted-text\">llamarse</span> (\"kuitwa\").</p>"}]},"inputType":null,"tests":[],"transcript":null,"scene":null,"translationPending":false}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/#es-a1-practice-first-questions","dashedName":"task-13","certification":"a1-professional-spanish","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"a1-professional-spanish","chapter":"es-a1-chapter-greetings-and-introductions","module":"es-a1-module-first-questions","block":"es-a1-practice-first-questions","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-first-questions/task-14","prevChallengePath":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-first-questions/task-12","id":"6910867bb3065a1924502732","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":22,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/a1-professional-spanish/es-a1-practice-first-questions/task-13"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}